  <sharedProfiles>
    <profile name="Emperor’s Talons" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="7901-894b-cf6d-d4ff">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">Reroll failed Resolve Tests made for any of your Adeptus Custodes units.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Technique: Dacatarai Flurry" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="6fe9-4c64-5a0c-36ea">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each weapon in this unit, instead of selecting a single target for that weapon, you may target each enemy unit within engagement range of this unit with that weapon.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Technique: Conservai Counter" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="60b1-040e-1e4b-3704">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">This unit gains Resilient 6+. After this unit gains this ability, if the active enemy unit is within 8” of and visible to this unit, that unit gains the following ability until the End step of the next turn:


Critical Opening: For each attack made by an Adeptus Custodes unit that targets this unit, a Hit Roll of 5+ for that attack causes an additional hit.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Technique: Kaptaris Parry" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="0c6b-2f19-8d96-a518">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each attack that targets this unit, after a failed Saving Throw for that attack, you may choose either ‘block’ or ‘deflect’ that attack. To block it, roll a D6. On a 3+, halve the D of that attack (rounding up). To deflect it, roll a D6. On a 5+, that attack fails.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Technique: Calistus Footwork" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="8a9c-3400-eaba-ca54">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">The type of each ranged weapon in this unit changes to Aslt. For each ranged attack this unit makes, reroll a Hit Roll of 1 and a Wound Roll of 1 for that attack. After this unit’s Attacks step, it may Fall Back up to 4”.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Technique: Rendax Thrust" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="0ffe-80e6-74fc-1c59">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While there is exactly one enemy unit within 4” of this unit, for each attack this unit makes which targets that unit, reroll a Hit Roll of 1 and a Wound Roll of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Martial Ka’tah" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="e499-7601-0c40-dc24">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After one of your Adeptus Custodes infantry units Activates, you may have that unit ‘perform a technique’.


After any enemy unit’s Move step, you may select one of your Adeptus Custodes infantry units and have that unit perform a technique.


To have a unit perform a technique, select one of the following ‘technique’ abilities. That unit gains the selected ability until the End step.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Infallible Instruction" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="62ce-f561-3981-5e38">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">Once per turn, after this unit Activates or finishes its Move step, you may select another one of your ready units visible to this unit. Then, this unit and the selected unit gain the following ability until the End step of the next turn:


Flawless Coordination: For each attack this unit makes, a Hit Roll of 6 for that attack causes an additional hit. After this unit’s End step, if this was not your second turn in a row, you may take another turn, and you must select a unit with Flawless Coordination to Activate that turn.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Golden Lightning" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="a983-2b14-2822-8f71">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit finishes a March, if that move ended at least 8” away from where it started, until the next time this unit Activates, for each attack that targets this unit, worsen the Hit Roll of that attack by 1.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
  </sharedProfiles>
</catalogue>
